                <head>737. Telegram 189 from Prague<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d737fn1"
                        >Source: Department of State, Central Files, 611.93/10–1956. Confidential;
                        Limit Distribution. Repeated to Geneva for Osborn as telegram 9.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Prague</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1956-10-19"
                            >October 19, 1956, 5 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <pb facs="d737-1" n="1" type="facsimile" xml:id="d737-1"/>
                <p>189. In order obtain maximum coverage and assist relations with press in Geneva
                    suggest that press officer Geneva be authorized make simultaneous release
                    proposed press statement on CHICOM implementation agreed announcement.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_JUA_1">
                            <hi rend="strong">Johnson</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
